Controls:
1. a, s, w, d to move the block left, down, right and up respectively
2. Tower view->2 
Helicopter View ->5
Top View - >1
Follow cam ->3
Tower view -> 0

extra feature:
Levels are given to choose from at the start of the game.
The winner if lost or won is displayed on the menu bar of the window.
Animated movements of block added.

